These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, fisherman, freelancer, software-developer
4 different games are played: poker, billiard, monopoly, canasta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, rock
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, brown, aquamarine, emerald
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, marigold, tulip, amaryllis
 1. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the fan of rock is between the dancer and the person who growsamaryllis##2
 3. the person who likes apricot is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 4. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is between the dancer and the fan of reggae##2
 6. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is the freelancer##1
 8. the software-developer is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the fan of folk is on the left of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Job           | freelancer | dancer   | software-developer | fisherman |
| Game   | poker      | billiard | monopoly              | canasta |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | funk     | rock               | reggae    |
| Color           | brown        | aquamarine     | emerald           | apricot       |
| Flower     | marigold | tulip     | dahlia                | amaryllis      |

