.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, rock-climbing, camping, dancing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, siglo, cain, swisher
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, subway, boat, jet-ski
4 different pets are kept: frog, goat, hamster, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 3. the siglo-smoker is between the person who's hobby is camping and the owner of the goat##2
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the siglo-smoker##1
 6. the cain-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the cain-smoker is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is camping##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Hobby          | camping       | rock-climbing      | traveling      | dancing      |
| Cigar           | swisher | siglo | cain | tiparillo |
| Transport   | jet-ski          | subway       | boat            | scooter      |
| Pet           | frog            | hamster    | goat           | snake       |
| Sport         | handball        | sailing    | tennis         | volleyball  |

