 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the bongani-smoker is the person who likes turquise##1
 9. the aristoff-smoker is between the person who likes apricot and the person playing backgammon##2
10. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
11. the person eating corn is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
