 3. the fan of indie is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 4. the owner of the rat is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is the person who growsrose##1
 6. the fan of indie is the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person watching goating movies##1
11. the person watching goating movies is between the person who growsrose and the owner of the lizard##2
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the owner of the rat and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | coffee         | lemonade | juice      |
| Flower           | rose | daffodil | zinnia | balloon-flower     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa         | indie          | ambient  | electronic |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster        | goating  | martial-arts | documentary   |
| Pet     | goat    | dog         | lizard     | rat     |

