.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, chess, whist, billiard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, august, october, april
4 different pets are kept: frog, goat, goldfish, snake
House: townhouse, cape-cod, art-deco, ranch-style
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, subway, trike
 1. the owner of the snake is between the art-deco house and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the cape-cod house is the person driving the subway##1
