 5. the ranch-style house is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the person playing billiard is between the person who's birthday is in april and the townhouse house##2

