The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, handball, parkour, sailing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, dahlia, begonia, daisy
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is the malaysian##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is between the thai and the person who's sport is badminton##2
 3. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who growsbegonia##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is the japanese##1
11. the japanese is the person who's sport is sailing##1

